Blackfang hurried to get inside the base and went straight to the med bay.

Blackfang: Hang in there, we'll do our best to save you.

--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, "raccoon7679" <raccoon7679@y...> wrote:
> Camoflage::
> 
> "Right! I'll go get Kenzo."  with that, she darted off towards the 
> base.  As she went, sh yelled "KENZO! KENZO! KENZO!" every twenty 
> feet or so untill she got to the base.
> 
> 
> KitKat::
> She groaned as she was picked up. Her body was limp as she had no 
> energy left to resist. She opened her optics slightly, and out of the 
> corner of her optic, she could see a male bot figure picking her up.  
> She couldn't tell who it was. But her wolf nose told her that it was 
> another wolf bot. She was about to try to talk when a surge of pain 
> ran through her belly. She threw her head back and arched her back in 
> writhing agony. "AAAHHHHHHHHH!" screaming out in anguish.
> 
> 
> --- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, "Nic" <Proudwing500k@h...> wrote:
> > The Maximal wolf looked at his Predacon opponent. He frowned but 
> made
> > no sign of outward defiance.
> > 
> > Blackfang: We will intervene quickly and bring her back to you fully
> > functional. In exchange, you must not leave the area or cause 
> trouble.
> > You know that an accident happens much too fast in surgeries...
> > 
> > With that, he transformed and took Kitkat in his arms, being careful
> > not to touch her where internal leaks were obvious.
> > 
> > Blackfang: Cam, head back to base now and warn Kenzo he's needed 
> right
> > away to help this bot. Go!
